flowchart TD
    Start([New Developer Onboarding]) --> CheckOS[Check OS Requirements]
    CheckOS --> InstallDeps[Install Dependencies]
    InstallDeps --> Qt[Install Qt 6]
    Qt --> CMake[Install CMake 3.16+]
    CMake --> Compiler[Install C++17 Compiler]
    Compiler --> Python[Install Python 3]
    Python --> CloneRepo[Clone Repository]
    CloneRepo --> SetEnv[Set Environment Variables]
    SetEnv --> ExportQt[Export DEFAULT_QT_PATH]
    ExportQt --> SourceScript[source scripts/setup_build_env.sh]
    SourceScript --> ConfigCMake[cmake -S . -B build]
    ConfigCMake --> ConfigOK{Configure OK?}
    ConfigOK -- Fail --> TroubleshootConfig[Troubleshoot Config]
    TroubleshootConfig --> ConfigCMake
    ConfigOK -- Pass --> BuildProject[cmake --build build -j8]
    BuildProject --> BuildOK{Build OK?}
    BuildOK -- Fail --> TroubleshootBuild[Troubleshoot Build]
    TroubleshootBuild --> BuildProject
    BuildOK -- Pass --> RunTests[ctest --output-on-failure]
    RunTests --> TestsOK{Tests Pass?}
    TestsOK -- Fail --> FixTests[Review Test Failures]
    FixTests --> RunTests
    TestsOK -- Pass --> RunApp[./build/src/z-monitor]
    RunApp --> AppRuns{App Runs?}
    AppRuns -- Fail --> TroubleshootRun[Troubleshoot Runtime]
    TroubleshootRun --> RunApp
    AppRuns -- Pass --> SetupIDE[Setup IDE/Editor]
    SetupIDE --> ConfigLinter[Configure Linters]
    ConfigLinter --> ReadDocs[Read Documentation]
    ReadDocs --> Ready[Developer Ready]
    Ready --> End([Setup Complete])
